;; cljfmt config for {{name}}.
;;
;; cljfmt (https://github.com/weavejester/cljfmt) is the de-facto
;; Clojure formatter — sensible defaults, editor integrations across
;; Calva / CIDER / Cursive, and a CLI for batch reformat.
;;
;; The defaults here are deliberately minimal: cljfmt's built-in
;; ruleset handles 95% of community Clojure idioms out of the box.
;; Override below as your team's house style firms up.
;;
;; Run from the project root:
;;
;;     # check (CI-friendly — non-zero exit on diff)
;;     clojure -M:cljfmt check
;;
;;     # rewrite in place
;;     clojure -M:cljfmt fix
;;
;; The `:cljfmt` alias in deps.edn wires up the dev-time CLI.
{:remove-multiple-non-indenting-spaces? false
 :remove-trailing-whitespace?           true
 :insert-missing-whitespace?            true}
